# Avatar System Configuration
# Supports TWO methods for avatar creation:
#
# METHOD 1: Automatic Generation (via Avaturn API)
# Users upload a photo → AI generates 3D avatar
#
# METHOD 2: Manual Uploads (MetaHuman Creator)
# Users export from MetaHuman Creator → Upload .glb file
# No configuration needed for MetaHuman

# For AUTOMATIC generation (optional), configure Avaturn:
VITE_AVATURN_API_KEY=your_api_key_from_avaturn_net
VITE_AVATURN_ENDPOINT=https://api.avaturn.net/

# If VITE_AVATURN_API_KEY is not set:
# - Automatic photo generation uses mock mode (development)
# - MetaHuman manual uploads still work (no API needed)

